      "instruction": "<p>Cut the<strong> lime<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong>&nbsp;into quarters</p>\r\n<p>Peel, top and tail, and cut the <strong>carrot<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span>&nbsp;</strong>into thin batons</p>\r\n<p>Deseed the<strong> red</strong>&nbsp;<strong>pepper<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong> (scrape the seeds and pith out with a teaspoon) and cut into bite-sized pieces</p>\r\n<p>Slice the <strong>mange tout</strong> into thin strips</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Lato; font-size: 15px; white-space: pre-wrap;\">&nbsp;</span></p>",
